diff_analysis.evidence: The changes are limited to generic type widening in FluentIterable.transformAndConcat, cleanup of ThreadLocal state in EventBus (adding eventsToDispatch.remove()), and annotation adjustments in Futures. None of these modifications involve input handling, web output, request handling, deserialization, SQL construction, or authorization logic, so they do not introduce CWE-79, CWE-352, CWE-502, CWE-89, or CWE-862 vulnerabilities.
